definitions.definition: Any of several common , often asymptomatic , sexually transmitted diseases caused by the microorganism Chlamydia trachomatis .
Any of various coccoid microorganisms of the genus Chlamydia that are pathogenic to humans and other animals .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) Any of several common , often asymptomatic , sexually transmitted diseases caused by the microorganism Chlamydia trachomatis .
secondary_definitions: ( countable ) Any of various coccoid microorganisms of the genus Chlamydia that are pathogenic to humans and other animals .
